<article id="post-2" class="post-2 page type-page status-publish hentry">
	<header class="entry-header">
		<h1 class="entry-title">Erie Protective Coatings</h1>
	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	<div class="entry-content">
		<div id="pl-2"  class="panel-layout" ><div id="pg-2-0"  class="panel-grid panel-no-style" ><div id="pgc-2-0-0"  class="panel-grid-cell" ><div id="panel-2-0-0-0" class="so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child" data-index="0" ><div class="so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base"><h3 class="widget-title">Industrial Finishing Services for Metal Industries</h3>
<div class="siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget">
	<p>EPC was incorporated in 1992 to provide Finishing Coating Services to Metal Industry both on a commercial basis or certified to Military Specifications.</p>
<p class="text">A partial list of the services offered by us is shown below:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.erieprotectivecoatings.com/index.php/structural-anodizing/">Clear and Color Anodizing</a><br />
(we can match to your color chips)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.erieprotectivecoatings.com/index.php/hardcoat-anodizing/">Hard Coat Anodizing including Teflon® impregnation </a>(Superimposed DC + AC Current)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.erieprotectivecoatings.com/index.php/selective-hard-anodizing/">Selective Hard Anodizing &amp; Masking</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.erieprotectivecoatings.com/index.php/chromate-coating/">Chromate Conversion (Irriditing Alodining)</a></li>
<li><a href="#">Polishing, Passivating &amp; Electropolishing<br />
of various metals</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.erieprotectivecoatings.com/index.php/black-oxide-electroless-nickel/">Electroless Nickel</a></li>
<li><a href="#">Black Oxide Misc. Steels and Stainless</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.erieprotectivecoatings.com/index.php/selective-hard-anodizing/">Plating of any metal substrate as well as selective plating on base metal</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.erieprotectivecoatings.com/index.php/lab-testing-services/">In-house Laboratory for Salt Spray Analysis &amp; Abrasion Testing</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
